　日\r\n                               書  記  官  李宜庭","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/111%2c%e5%98%89%e7%b0%a1%2c563%2c20220630%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,111,嘉簡,563,20220630,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"嘉簡","JNO":"563","JDATE":"20220630","JTITLE":"公然侮辱"}